            <text type="postcard" decls="#corresp1">
                <body>
                    <div type="message">

                        <opener>
                            <address>
                <addrLine>Piaras Béaslaí, 25 Lindsay Rd, <del>L</del> Glasnevin, <hi rend="underline">Dublin</hi></addrLine>
                </address>
                            <dateline><date when="1916-01-11">11-1-16</date></dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p> Annso dhom arís &amp; uaigneas orm indiaidh B. Átha Cliath. Níor bhuail
                            an taingeal liom. Is dóca go raibh sé imthighte go luath. Ar thugais
                            cuairt ar P. Ó Shoin. Abair le Tadgh Scannell an rud sin a dhéanamh </p>
                        <closer><signed>M.</signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    <div type="imageCaption">
                        <pb n="2" facs="#L1916_267_img_2"/>
                        <p>"Donegal Square &amp; Wellington Place, Belfast."</p>

                    </div>
                </body>
